`nette.ajax.js`
**********

Alternativní obslužný skript pro AJAX. .[perex]

|* Github | https://github.com/vojtech-dobes/nette.ajax.js
|* Bug reporty,<br>feature requesty | https://github.com/vojtech-dobes/nette.ajax.js/issues
